site.name: Lemmy.world
site.sidebar:
Lemmy.world is a general-purpose Lemmy instance of various topics, for the entire world to use.

Be polite and follow the rules (https://mastodon.world/about).

## Get started

See the [Getting Started Guide](https://lemmy.world/post/37906)

## Donations
If you would like to make a donation to support the cost of running this platform, please do so at the mastodon. world donation URLs:

- https://opencollective.com/mastodonworld
- https://patreon.com/mastodonworld

## Questions / Issues
Questions/issues can be posted [here](https://lemmy.world/c/support) or emailed to info@lemmy.world. Reporting is to be done via the reporting button under a post/comment.
